import re
f = open('abs1.txt','r')   #opens the file
line = f.read()
j = 0
sub = re.findall('.*\n',line)   #uses Regular Expression
while 1:
        try:
            line = sub[j]
        except:
            break        
        if line:
            open("abs1_sub_para/file " + str(j + 1) + ".txt", 'w').write(line)
            j = j + 1
f.close()      #closes the file
